	<text>
		<body>
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002108_0001"><!--pb/@n='88r'--></pb>
<lb/><p rend="center"><placeName>Newstead Abbey</placeName>
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="town">Mansfield</settlement></placeName>, <placeName><region> <choice><abbr>Notts.</abbr><expan>Nottinghamshire</expan></choice></region></placeName></p><!-- First two lines are type-written header for stationery HB 9/27/12 -->
<lb/><p rend="right"><date when="1864-11-08">8 <choice><abbr>Nov<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi></abbr><expan>November</expan></choice> 1864</date></p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My dear <persName>Waller</persName></p>
<lb/><p>With most
<lb/>profound grief the
<lb/>suspicion arises in
<lb/>my mind that you
<lb/>are a muff. I
<lb/>wrote a long time
<lb/>ago asking you
<lb/>to give me the
<lb/>sketches &amp;c which
<lb/>in a moment of
<lb/>weakness you

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002108_0002"><!--pb/@n='88v'--></pb>
<lb/>promised me. Tell
<lb/>me if you never
<lb/>had any - but <choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice>
<lb/>think to get off in
<lb/>silence. You will
<lb/>never hear anything
<lb/>like the end of it
<lb/>Well after this
<lb/>preamble which
<lb/>you are to read in
<lb/>a very angry tone
<lb/>can you give me
<lb/>a sketch of the little
<lb/>loom for wea<gap agent="damage" extent="3" unit="chars"/><supplied cert="high">ving</supplied>
<lb/>cotton which y<gap agent="damage" extent="2" unit="chars"/><supplied cert="high">ou</supplied>

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_002108_0003"><!--pb/@n='89r'--></pb>
<lb/>sent home - it was
<lb/>made by one of the
<lb/>boys. also if
<lb/>you can a furnace 
<lb/>for <term type="occupation">smelting</term> iron
<lb/>or anything else
<lb/>you like and
<lb/>write &amp; say if
<lb/>you can or can
<lb/>not please</p>
<lb/><p><persName>Agnes</persName> is wishing
<lb/>you to get her
<lb/>insects set up
<lb/>I shall pay you
<lb/><gap agent="damage"/><!-- cannot make out words on line because cut off from page HB 12/29/11 -->

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_002108_0004"><!--pb/@n='89v'--></pb>
<lb/>tell <persName>M<hi rend="sup underline">r</hi> Stewart</persName> that
<lb/>you were the man
<lb/>who said there was
<lb/>no <term type="plant">cotton bushes</term>
<lb/>all the way up to
<lb/><placeName><settlement type="village">Magomero</settlement></placeName> &amp; beyond
<lb/>of course you did
<lb/>I am writing <unclear cert="medium">just</unclear>
<lb/>between the light
<lb/>and dark &amp; only
<lb/>by way of saying
<lb/>to <unclear>on dye do</unclear> - saw
<lb/><placeName>S S Oxon</placeName>. &amp; spoke a <!-- Do not know how to code or expand SS Oxon. HB 12/29/11 --><!-- I think it refers to the name of a school AM -->
<lb/>few words at <placeName><region><w>Nott<supplied>-</supplied>
<lb break="no"/>ingham</w></region></placeName> very much</p>
			
</div>
